Name: 1st Anniversary Coin
AttributesDescription: A kind of commemorative coin that can be used to buy supplies and rewards from Abbowser.
BgDescription: An event token commemorating the first anniversary of the Second Coming of Solaris's beta test. The tail was intended to feature the Pioneer Association's logo, but somehow, it bears Abbowser's portrait instead. It seems Abbowser has taken a particular interest in this coin.
ObtainedShowDescription: A kind of commemorative coin that can be used to buy supplies and rewards from Abbowser.
